<div class="mdui-typo"><h1 id="conscience-n">conscience <strong><em>n</em></strong></h1>
<p>英 /'kɒnʃəns/    美 /'kɑːnʃəns/  </p>
<h2 id="_1">释义</h2>
<h4 id="1-c-u">1.★ <strong>[C] &amp; [U] 良心；良知：</strong></h4>
<div class="mdui-typo"><blockquote><p>have a <strong>guilty / bad conscience</strong>
问心有愧</p></div>

<div class="mdui-typo"><blockquote><p>have a <strong>clear / good conscience</strong>
问心无愧</p></div></div>